  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to analyze the effects of an exercise program in the pulmonary function,
      cardiorespiratory fitness, diet quality index, physical activity, body composition, muscle
      function, agility, and psychological health in a group of children with asthma and
      respiratory symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
