    <description>A two month intervention program 3 days/week will be carried out. The session will last ~60 minutes, and will consist of a combined training (aerobic training ~30 min, and strength ~30 min of 7 whole body exercises (3 sets x 10 repetitions at 70-80% of their maximum).</description>
